editorialNotes.standard: Nothing beats a kid-friendly game that keeps the whole family captivatedand Toca has us snipping, straightening, and styling to our heart's content. Once we've perfected our customer's silly new dos, we make sure to add some accessories, snap a pic, and share the hair.

ios.subtitle: Create to show what you know!

editorialNotes.standard: Weve played so many games that we feel like we could create our ownand now we can, all without coding classes or complex tutorials. With this ingenious educational app, it's easy to become a designer. Imagination rules as you build characters, worlds and stories for one-of-a-kind games meant to be saved, shared andof courseplayed.

name: Word Wizard for Kids School Ed

editorialNotes.standard: What are those towers that touch the sky? Tinybops awesome sandbox teaches kids the fun wayby letting them build, watch, and play. As they add floors and test the effects of plumbing problems and earthquakes, they're actually learning basic design and engineering principles. Amazing details aboundfrom all the busy little inhabitants to the full-blown skyline you can make.

name: Cosmolander - Missions in the Solar System

editorialNotes.standard: Were having Jupiter-sized fun with this educational spin around the solar system. Cosmolander brings fascinating facts about the planets to life with colorful artwork and animated quizzes that play like video games. Best of all, theres a wealth of real scientific information to be discovered, so the entire family can share in learning more about our cosmic backyard.
